:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3376:\"<p>The SiteOrigin Premium Mirror Widgets addon allows you to create a widget once and use it everywhere. When the Mirror Widget is updated, changes reflect in all instances of the widget.</p>\n<p>Mirror Widgets can be inserted into any Page Builder page or widget sidebar area using the dedicated widget.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_176845\" style=\"width: 1832px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-176845\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-176845 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1822\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget.png 1822w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-300x64.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-768x164.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-699x150.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-1050x225.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/adding-siteorigin-mirror-widget-313x67.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1822px) 100vw, 1822px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-176845\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add Mirror Widgets to a page or theme sidebar area using the dedicated widget.</p></div>\n<p>SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.19.0</code> adds the ability to insert Mirror Widgets using a shortcode. Mirror Widget shortcodes can be inserted into <strong>any page, post, or widget</strong> allowing for greater content management flexibility. Widgets that support shortcodes include the SiteOrigin Editor, Features, and Price Table to name a few.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_297739\" style=\"width: 1646px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-297739\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1636\" height=\"667\" class=\"size-full wp-image-297739\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode.jpg 1636w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-300x122.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-699x285.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-768x313.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-1536x626.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-1050x428.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/mirror-widgets-shortcode-313x128.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1636px) 100vw, 1636px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-297739\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mirror Widgets shortcodes are available in the archive and single post view.</p></div>\n<p>Already using SiteOrigin Premium? Find out more about using the Mirror Widgets addon in the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/mirror-widgets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">premium documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/insert-mirror-widgets-using-shortcodes/\">Insert Mirror Widgets Using Shortcodes</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{